00:44:09,130 --> 00:44:10,800
Five!

652
00:44:13,300 --> 00:44:14,430
Six!

653
00:44:16,300 --> 00:44:17,510
Seven!

654
00:44:19,310 --> 00:44:21,890
Eight!

655
00:44:21,980 --> 00:44:23,350
Nine!

656
00:44:24,980 --> 00:44:26,400
Ten!

