00:44:48,670 --> 00:44:50,590
Thanks.
You read my mind.

660
00:44:52,380 --> 00:44:55,510
Oh, third watch always
seems to last forever.

661
00:44:55,590 --> 00:44:57,260
I don't know.

662
00:44:57,340 --> 00:44:59,850
It depends on who
you're spending it with.

663
00:45:02,600 --> 00:45:04,430
Something's wrong.

664
