677
00:45:59,160 --> 00:46:02,530
We're way ahead of the curve
in every department.

678
00:46:02,580 --> 00:46:05,620
I can anticipate you.

679
00:46:05,660 --> 00:46:08,460
You know what I want.

680
00:46:10,080 --> 00:46:13,380
