1427
01:58:53,610 --> 01:58:56,370
Soldiers like Private Ace Levy
and Lieutenant John Rico.

1428
01:58:56,450 --> 01:58:59,950
Come on, you apes!
You wanna live forever?

1429
01:59:00,040 --> 01:59:01,500
We need you all.

